_definition.iso_639_3_eng: This namespace covers user interface elements that display elements of the core dictionary in a table of contents.

_description.iso_639_3_eng: The *data dictionary* is constituted by a *variety of terms*: *namespaces*, *descriptors*, *enumerations* and *structures*, this *namespace* is used to *prefix* items that will *constitute* the *tables of content* for these *core dictionary elements*.

_definition.iso_639_3_eng: Core data dictionary controlled vocabulary definitions.
